nodes.text: Umate was the highest mountain in the Manarai range on Coruscant, and by the Republic Era, the only uncovered mountain on the ecumenopolis. The mountain's body, below the plaza, was incorporated into the city-planet's fabric, becoming riddled with tunnels. Umate's peak, the centrepiece of Monument Plaza, became a popular visiting spot for tourists, and during her term of office, Supreme Chancellor Lina Soh liked to visit the spot as well.
